text: Kuchukovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Ilchigulovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 72 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 92 km from Uchaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Kuchukovo
